1. Open datebase repository

https://github.com/offensive-security/exploitdb

2.Clone the database repository

sudo git clone  https://gitlab.com/exploit-database/exploitdb.git

NOTE: Example clone it in Documents

3.Create a symbolic link to use this functionality anywhere in the system

sudo ln -sf /home/samuraii/Documents/exploitdb/searchsploit /usr/local/bin/searchsploit

NOTE: If you need to remove a symbolic link, you can use the next comand

sudo unlink /usr/local/bin/searchsploit 

it's same 

sudo unlink "HERE YOUR SYMBOLIC PATH"
 
